            "title": "強強聯手 網飛將以現金加股票交易收購華納兄弟",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"強強聯手 網飛將以現金加股票交易收購華納兄弟\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"719\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/3XC1Hxe1ovMVgExWBpCKKQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTcxOTtjZj13ZWJw/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2025-12/f6d9cfb0-d258-11f0-aef6-1d15b01cc9e6\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">強強聯手 網飛將以現金加股票交易收購華納兄弟</figcaption></div></figure></div>",
