        {
            "title": "養老金法案成功通關 德國總理默茨暫時擺脫危機",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"養老金法案成功通關 德國總理默茨暫時擺脫危機\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"621\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/EGFJezmEQuVL3M7_nYFfXg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYyMTtjZj13ZWJw/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2025-12/0572b250-d243-11f0-9fe9-724d9defc896\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">養老金法案成功通關 德國總理默茨暫時擺脫危機</figcaption></div></figure></div>",
